{"tid":1076580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒錢沒老婆！　45歲大叔存款11K嘆「悲慘人生」","createTime":"2019-03-25T03:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T12:29:48.000Z","uid":121473,"like":95,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"26c0fc87e06d9ab5e0bcda67f7e3314e4bae9eaf","tid":1076580,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"你認為45歲應該有多少資產？一名單身的男子因為已45歲，但卻幾乎無存款，還過著無穩定工作的生活，向朋友吐苦水「悲慘人生。」引起網友討論，「難道存款代表一切嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wh7nWaD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwh7nWaD.jpg&h=51f8021a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒錢沒老婆，45歲大叔存款只有11K嘆「悲慘人生」。翻攝爆怨公社<br />\n<br />\n網友將朋友的情況PO至《臉書》社團「爆怨公社」，表示朋友已經45歲，自嘲無穩定工作，就連5萬都拿不出來，覺得人生悲哀，讓他語塞。<br />\n<br />\n男子的情況引起網友討論，有人認為「45歲真的母湯」、但也有人認為「看他想過怎樣的人生而已 ，沒有對錯」、「不要影響到親人就好」、「很多中年人也沒存款沒負債，沒癌症身體健康就行了。明天會發生什麼事 誰都不知道。」<br />\n<br />\n另有一堆人路過比慘，「我戶頭剩8塊啦」、「30初路過存款16元」、「我認識一位48歲，月光族，為了籌20萬想破頭，完全沒存款。」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190325/1539205/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3TeTh3nSd7khcIZfLM9qPfbZLebwM1wVh0rDM47qNoBGASFwNELDySpa0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190325%2F1539205%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3TeTh3nSd7khcIZfLM9qPfbZLebwM1wVh0rDM47qNoBGASFwNELDySpa0&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6bhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=f6c8244c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190325%2F1539205%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3TeTh3nSd7khcIZfLM9qPfbZLebwM1wVh0rDM47qNoBGASFwNELDySpa0&h=57b8fd70\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190